            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Nymphis <lb n="2"/>Medicis <lb n="3"/>sacrum <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius Commodu<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> <lb n="5"/>Orfitianus <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der linken Nebenseite Griffschale, Rosette, vegetabile Ornamente; auf der rechten Nebenseite Krug auf Efeublättern, vegetabile Ornamente. Z. 1: HI-Ligatur; Z. 3: VM-Ligatur. Datierung: wahrscheinlicher Zeitraum der Statthalterschaft des C. Iulius Commodus Orfitianus.</p>
            </div>
